<p>
<lb n="1"/>tiripuvanaccakkaravattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> virarā<hi rend="grantha">je</hi>ntiratevaṟku yāṇ
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṭu Irupattonpatāvatu perunāṭṭil muṭṭamāna
<lb n="3" break="no"/><unclear>ama</unclear>rapuyaṅkaranallūril viyāpāri maṉṟāṭi marutan mutaliyāṉa vaṇikacakkarava
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ttiyen Avināciyāḷuṭaiyār kūttāṭuvāṟku tiru <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ṟukiḻā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṉaṭikku yiṭṭamutukku Arici kuṟuṇikku viṭṭanilam kola <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ṟaiyil
<lb n="6"/>manṟāṭṭu nilam kāṇik kellai nam viṭṭu nilattukku
<lb n="7" break="no"/>m maṇalivaṇika nilattukku vaṭakku vāykkālukku kiḻak
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ku tevatānattukkut teṟku nāṅkellaikkuṭpaṭṭa In
<lb n="9" break="no"/>nilaṅkāṇiyum kuṭutten Ittanmam cantirātittavarai
<lb n="10"/>ce(o)lvatāka viṭṭukkuṭutten vaṇikaccakkaravattiyan ma
<lb n="11" break="no"/><unclear>ru</unclear>tu paṉmā<hi rend="grantha">heśvararakṣai <g type="ddanda">.</g></hi>
</p>

